de.ityx.mediatrix.api

Interface IServerAPI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MediatrixServerAPI

    public interface IServerAPI
    English:
    The API for the server provides the communication channel with the database. The requests to the database run using the interface. Each object as return value from a "get...API()" function is a singleton. The APIs are separated based on the object art. E.g. the storing, loading and search for questions are processed in the object implements ISQuestion. How to use: API.getServerAPI().FunctionName(...);
